        "en": "<p>You require Flemish recognition as an environmental coordinator if you perform this function for two or more different companies and you are not an employee of the operator. You can be recognised at level A or level B: the environmental impact of the company determines which level of environmental coordinator must be appointed.</p><p>The Department of the Environment and Spatial Development website lists recognised environmental coordinators. <a href=\"https://datasets.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/be.vl.omgeving.erkenningen.distribution.milieucoordinatoren.pdf\">Download the overview list</a>. </p>",
